                    "title": "Foundation & TensorFlow",
                    "desc": "\n                <p><strong>Goal:</strong> Build a rock-solid foundation in the core principles of a Lead AI Researcher. Dedicate the first two months entirely to mastering <b>TensorFlow</b> through hands-on tutorials and basic projects.</p>\n                <div style=\"margin-top: 8px;\">\n                    <strong>Focus Areas:</strong>\n                    <ul style=\"margin-top: 4px; padding-left: 20px; color: var(--text-secondary);\">\n                        <li>Setting up your professional development environment.</li>\n                        <li>Deep-diving into the foundational syntax, theories, or rules of TensorFlow.</li>\n                        <li>Understanding the daily operations and business value of Lead AI Researchers.</li>\n                    </ul>\n                </div>\n                <div style=\"margin-top: 8px;\">\n                    <strong>Action Item:</strong> Complete at least three \"Hello World\" or equivalent introductory projects from scratch.\n                </div>"
