                    "desc": "\n                <p><strong>Goal:</strong> Tackle professional-grade scenarios. Focus on optimization, scalability, and leveraging <b>Facebook Ads</b> alongside Analytics, Social Media, Leadership, Mentoring, Strategy to build robust systems.</p>\n                <div style=\"margin-top: 8px;\">\n                    <strong>Focus Areas:</strong>\n                    <ul style=\"margin-top: 4px; padding-left: 20px; color: var(--text-secondary);\">\n                        <li>Performance optimization, refactoring, and advanced architectural decisions.</li>\n                        <li>Incorporating secondary tools like Analytics, Social Media, Leadership, Mentoring, Strategy into an automated workflow.</li>\n                        <li>Studying and reverse-engineering real-world, production-level examples.</li>\n                    </ul>\n                </div>\n                <div style=\"margin-top: 8px;\">\n                    <strong>Action Item:</strong> Contribute to an open-source project or refactor your MVP to handle scale and edge-cases.\n                </div>"
